OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784319520
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,CCoventry murder
OL,6,FOfficers investigating the murder of
OL,7,FMichael Ababio in Coventry have made
OL,8,Fanother arrest.
OL,10,FA 29-year-old man was arrested in
OL,11,FHillfields on Thursday 16 July on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,14,FHe was released on police bail as the
OL,15,Finvestigation continues.
OL,17,FFour people have so far been charged
OL,18,Fin connection with Michael's death,
OL,19,Fwhich happened on 22 February near
OL,20,FFoleshill Library.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/2
