PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784319520
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,CCoventry murder
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police said: "Detectives
OL,7,Ffrom our Homicide unit have worked
OL,8,Fround the clock to gather evidence and
OL,9,Fspeak to witnesses as part of their
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,F"Anyone who saw what happened and
OL,13,Fhasn't yet come forward to speak can
OL,14,Fdo so by calling 101 quoting log 4185
OL,15,Fof 22 February.
OL,17,F"We take knife crime and carrying a
OL,18,Fweapon seriously. If you know someone
OL,19,Fwho is carrying a weapon, please call
OL,20,Fus on 101 to report."
